    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;L/Right Reflection&quot; is an RPG game in which the main character, who is unable to use offensive sorcery, battles by reflecting enemy attacks.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312040/extras/364d4cd2e3d84c776f412dbca59fa9a6.poster.avif?t=1693052769\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312040/extras/364d4cd2e3d84c776f412dbca59fa9a6.webm?t=1693052769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312040/extras/364d4cd2e3d84c776f412dbca59fa9a6.mp4?t=1693052769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The player controls Lumis, a girl who is a sorcerer but cannot use offensive sorcery. How will Lumis defeat the enemies even if she can't attack?<br>The way Lumis defeats the enemies is through reflection sorcery. You can damage the enemy by reflecting the enemy's attack at the right moment.<br><br>In the battle, enemy attacks are represented by a skill cursor, which looks like a magic circle. At the center of the battle screen, there is an area called a marker. When the skill cursor is just over the marker, press the button for a successful reflection. The game is designed in the style of a rhythm game, in which the player parries the movement of the skill cursor to move in various ways, such as straight lines, curves, waves, and rotations.<br><br>Also, there is not only one button to press but three different buttons. The enemies use three types of attacks: blows, slashes, and magic, so press the button corresponding to each attack to reflect them.<br><br><strong>Sorcery</strong><br>In addition to reflection sorcery, Lumis can also use sorcery to advance the battle. Such as,<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Reflective damage is reduced but slows down the enemy's attack.<br></li><li> Reduces HP by half but increases reflective damage<br></li><li> Automatically reflect all enemy attacks for one turn, but reflective damage becomes a little</li></ul><br>These consume MP, but many of them have more powerful effects.<br><br><strong>Characters</strong><br>This game uses Live2D, so the characters move vividly in conversation and battle scenes! Especially in conversation scenes, the characters' expressions change in detail, making the story more enjoyable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312040/extras/d46bd636a577950e92e9fa8cc5542f31.poster.avif?t=1693052769\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312040/extras/d46bd636a577950e92e9fa8cc5542f31.webm?t=1693052769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312040/extras/d46bd636a577950e92e9fa8cc5542f31.mp4?t=1693052769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
